      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: GameText
      value: "<b>Wizardry: Proving Grounds of the Mad Overlord (1981). </b>\n\nParty
        of up to 6 characters. \n-5 different races\n-3 alignments\n-4 basic classes\n-4
        advanced classes \n\u2013 inspired by <b>Dungeons and Dragons 1st Edition.</b>
        (Roddison, 2024). \n\nExplore, find treasure, level up by killing monsters,
        and then fight the last boss at the bottom of the level to get a powerful
        amulet.\n\nParty system and spell-slot system inspired the team behind <b>Final
        Fantasy</b> (Square, 1987) (Parish, 2017)\n\nThe random enemy encounters
        also later contributed to the creation of <b>Dragon Quest</b> (Enix, Spike
        Chunsoft, 1986). (Kalata, 2008).\n"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
